<i>Spring and summer.</i>

541
00:38:25,680 --> 00:38:27,960
<i>Autumn and winter.</i>

542
00:39:43,940 --> 00:39:50,520
<i>Since that incident, she had been sleeping on the beam and wouldn't trust anyone anymore.</i>

543
00:39:50,520 --> 00:39:52,340
<i>I may understand the pain in her heart.</i>

544
00:39:52,340 --> 00:39:58,060
<i>But she had become increasingly rebellious, to the point where even I'm afraid of her.</i>

545
00:39:58,900 --> 00:40:03,900
<i>I even suspect that she might really be the ominous person.</i>

546
00:40:03,900 --> 00:40:09,980
So I had to lock her up in Zhaolu Hall and guard her strictly to prevent any trouble.

547
00:40:11,180 --> 00:40:14,080
In reality, you've been protecting her all along.

548
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:16,260
I'm powerless.

549
00:40:16,980 --> 00:40:22,020
The Grand Chancellor is a senior who has served three dynasties, is deeply rooted in the court, and highly respected.

550
00:40:22,640 --> 00:40:25,720
I wanted to do more for her, but I lack the ability to do it.

551
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:29,340
Fortunately, she met you.

552
00:40:30,080 --> 00:40:32,920
Since you're determined to protect her,

553
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:37,100
