554
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:53,880
Why are you only saying this now?

555
00:40:57,320 --> 00:41:00,020
I was terrified.

556
00:41:00,820 --> 00:41:04,200
I was terrified that you're an ill-fated person who will harm the human race.

557
00:41:04,980 --> 00:41:07,760
I also feared you might lose your life.

558
