563
00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:30,340
I don't care how others treat me in the palace.

564
00:41:30,340 --> 00:41:33,300
But you broke my heart the most.

565
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:37,240
You also saw me as an ill-fated person.

566
00:41:37,240 --> 00:41:41,420
