568
00:41:45,080 --> 00:41:48,380
I dared not say it.

569
00:41:48,380 --> 00:41:51,400
I was afraid if I show compassion only once, it would lead to suspicion and criticism from the ministers.

570
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:53,280
The truth is...

571
